	<div class="contentwide">
		<h2>Summary:</h2><div class="infobox">Agents may conduct one (at a time) of several covert missions once in an enemy city. Note that some of these missions are restricted to performance by a player with a specific Affinity.<br /><br />Missions:<br /><br />- Establish Network: Low risk, low difficulty. Once a Network is established, extra information is shown in the Intel Report. The higher the rank of the Agent, the more information about the City is displayed.<br /><br />- Siphon Energy: Low risk, medium difficulty. Steal Energy from the targeted City.<br /><br />- Propaganda Campaign: Low risk, low difficulty. Player gains Diplomatic Capital.<br /><br />- Steal Research: Low risk, medium difficulty. Steals research.<br /><br />- Recruit Defectors: Low risk, medium difficulty. Gives the player a set of random Military Units at the Capital.<br /><br />- Steal Technology: Medium risk, medium difficulty. Steals Technology from the targeted player.<br /><br />- Hack Satellites: Medium risk, high difficulty. De-orbits Satellites belonging to the targeted player within 5 tiles of the City in which the mission was performed in.<br /><br />- Coup D'etat: High risk, high difficulty. Grants the targeted City to the player.<br /><br />- Collossus Strike: High risk, high difficulty. Draws hostile Aliens to the targeted City. This mission requires levels in the <span class="color_harmony_affinity">Harmony</span> Affinity.<br /><br />- Dirty Bomb: High risk, high difficulty. Sets off a bomb in the targeted City, decreasing its population drastically. This mission requires levels in the <span class="color_purity_affinity">Purity</span> Affinity.<br /><br />- Sabotage: High risk, high difficulty. Pillages nearby improvements. This mission requires levels in the <span class="color_supremacy_affinity">Supremacy</span> Affinity.</div>
